title: War of the Roses: A Neighborhood Affair
description: Eve found her boyfriend Cameron doing something with the neighbor that left her in disbelief and now she's wondering if the two of them are having an affair.  Cameron tries to explain how "neighborly" he was being but it feels like it's more than just being a good neighbor.
